<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Oakmount Truck Dispatch Services</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        header {
            background: #ff6600;
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .service-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .service-section h2 {
            color: #ff6600;
        }
        form {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        input, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        button {
            background: #ff6600;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>USA Truck Dispatch Services</h1>
        <p>Your Reliable Truck Dispatch Partner Nationwide</p>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="service-section">
            <h2>Our Services</h2>
            <p>We provide top-notch truck dispatch services across the USA, ensuring seamless load management and timely deliveries.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="service-section">
            <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>24/7 Dispatch Support</li>
                <li>Competitive Rates</li>
                <li>Experienced Team</li>
                <li>Efficient Load Management</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="service-section">
            <h2>Latest Industry News</h2>
            <p><strong>How AI is Transforming Truck Dispatching in 2025</strong></p>
            <p>With the latest advancements in artificial intelligence and automation, truck dispatching has become more efficient than ever. AI-powered logistics solutions are helping companies reduce costs, optimize routes, and enhance driver safety. As the industry embraces digital transformation, dispatchers can now make data-driven decisions to ensure timely deliveries and minimize downtime.</p>
            <p>Stay updated with our blog for more insights on the evolving trucking landscape.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="service-section">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (123) 456-7890</p>
            <p><strong>Email:</strong> contact@oakmountdispatch.com</p>
            <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Dispatch Lane, New York, NY, USA</p>
            <form>
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                
                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                
                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="4" required></textarea>
                
                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Oakmount Truck Dispatch Services. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>